                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, effective bandages are much more than just rags. I will be demonstrating the difference and then you will have the last half hour of class to make bandages and take some away with you.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
